** Junior Mining Consultant **

** About Us **

Founded 37 years ago, Micromine is a leading provider of next generation
technology for the global mineral resources industry. With 22 international
offices, we are one of the world's premier mining software companies, with our
solutions used in more than 90 countries, including over 50 active mine sites
and 3,000 diverse projects.

** What We Offer **

A dynamic multinational company, on a high growth trajectory, with the
benefits of an established market leading business:

  * Opportunities for professional development and progression. 
  * Free gym membership. 
  * Discounted private health insurance. 
  * A team first culture and the chance to work with cutting edge mining software. 

** About The Opportunity **

Our Precision Consulting Team leverage their deep industry experience to
enable clients to optimise their operations and reduce costs. As the company
continues to thrive, an opening has become available for a Junior Mining
Consultant at our Brisbane, Fortitude Valley office.

In this role you will work very closely with Senior Consultants to create
customised solutions for our mining clients. Other responsibilities will
include:

  * Work closely with our mining clients to gather requirements and consult on projects. 
  * Use those requirements to script customised solutions within the Micromine Spry software using C#. 
  * Provide general technical input as part of the Precision Consulting business, including training and product development. 
  * Building client relationships and identifying further opportunities. 
  * Contribute to the ongoing enhancement of the Micromine software. 

** About You **

In this Junior Mining Consultant position you will have a tertiary degree in
engineering with experience and/or interest in the mining industry.

Other key skills, experience, and qualifications:

  * Very good communication and interpersonal skills. 
  * Understanding or experience within mining will be highly desirable. 
  * Comfortable with periodic travel to client mine site. 
  * Scripting experience in C# is a bonus 
  * Consulting experience is a bonus 

** Next Steps **

If you are looking to make a meaningful impact on our clients whilst helping
mentor junior engineers, we encourage you to apply for this opportunity.

To learn more or apply, visit our website at www.micromine.com.

